State Management
The package uses BLoC pattern for state management:
SearchBloc: Manages search state and filtering
PaymentBloc: Handles payment processing state
MapBloc: Manages map interactions and markers
SyncBloc: Handles admin synchronization

Error Handling
Comprehensive error handling with:
Network error recovery
Payment failure handling
Location permission errors
API error management
User-friendly error messages

Performance
Lazy loading for images and data
Efficient pagination
Memory management
Network request optimization
Cache implementation

